title: Occult - Crystal, Gem, and Metal Magic (pdf) EarthBow
description:
Cunningham, Scott - Encyclopedia of Crystal, Gem, and Metal Magic, 1996, 236 pages

Cunningham's book is a great reference for anyone involved in this type of magick. It includes extensive information about the major magickal stones and metals, as well as how to cleanse, charge, and use them.


Note: I will be adding many more titles soon, Search for "EarthBow" for a list of available titles.

As always, comments (good or bad) are appreciated
